[{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/16/78/167817.jpg","floor":"#2","id":"1472667","time":"2019-8-2 10:41","userId":"167817","userName":"山田家","userSign":"","message":"不太可能，毕竟拼接的图片大部分都是选择白天的图像<br>因为晚上一片黑啊！","sub":[{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/00/34/3490.jpg","floor":"#2-1","id":"1472716","time":"2019-8-2 11:48","userId":"lhb5883","userName":"lhb5883-污🐱王VIP⑩","userSign":"","message":"+1"}]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/30/42/304246.jpg","floor":"#3","id":"1472718","time":"2019-8-2 11:51","userId":"304246","userName":"Rくん","userSign":"(答えはいつも私の胸に～)","message":"能不能取决于太湖这块镜子够不够大，在开始计算之前我的直观感受是应该不够。","sub":[{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/13/30/133075.jpg","floor":"#3-1","id":"1472773","time":"2019-8-2 13:07","userId":"liaune","userName":"君寻","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">Rくん</span> 说: 我算了一下，大约轨道高度低于6000km的话，是有可能在太湖里看到月亮的。<br>但同步轨道35000km还多，是看不到的。</q></div>中低轨道卫星高度一般在1000km以下，高轨道卫星都是通讯用的，不对地面成像。"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/00/34/3490.jpg","floor":"#3-2","id":"1472780","time":"2019-8-2 13:23","userId":"lhb5883","userName":"lhb5883-污🐱王VIP⑩","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">Rくん</span> 说: 我算了一下，大约轨道高度低于6000km的话，是有可能在太湖里看到月亮的。<br>然后又查了一下高分卫星系列的轨道高度，600km多点，应该有可能拍到。</q></div>主要还是角度问题 月亮和卫星要在水面上角度对称"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/00/34/3490.jpg","floor":"#3-3","id":"1472817","time":"2019-8-2 14:08","userId":"lhb5883","userName":"lhb5883-污🐱王VIP⑩","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">Rくん</span> 说: 卫星能在晚上飞跃太湖和月球之间就够了。</q></div>你要考虑角度,如果只是拍月光够了 但是要成像还是有点难度."},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/00/34/3490.jpg","floor":"#3-4","id":"1472837","time":"2019-8-2 14:31","userId":"lhb5883","userName":"lhb5883-污🐱王VIP⑩","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">Rくん</span> 说: 所以我说“飞跃太湖和月球之间”</q></div>月球不一定能在太湖正上方 你这个条件太严格了."},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/00/34/3490.jpg","floor":"#3-5","id":"1472841","time":"2019-8-2 14:37","userId":"lhb5883","userName":"lhb5883-污🐱王VIP⑩","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">Rくん</span> 说: 月球和地面之间确定一条线段，交轨道高度球面于一点。我觉得我是这个意思。</q></div>满足反射定律就够了 你那条线段不好满足."},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/00/34/3490.jpg","floor":"#3-6","id":"1472843","time":"2019-8-2 14:38","userId":"lhb5883","userName":"lhb5883-污🐱王VIP⑩","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">Rくん</span> 说: 月球和地面之间确定一条线段，交轨道高度球面于一点。我觉得我是这个意思。</q></div>虽然从比例上来说也就是扩充成了个面而已."},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/31/34/313469.jpg","floor":"#3-7","id":"1473008","time":"2019-8-2 17:56","userId":"313469","userName":"Cedar","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">lhb5883-污&#x1F431;王VIP⑩</span> 说: 满足反射定律就够了 你那条线段不好满足.</q></div>还要考虑大气折射 说不定看到的月亮是歪的"}]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/icon.jpg","floor":"#4","id":"1472735","time":"2019-8-2 12:27","userId":"483996","userName":"二次元熊猫会有三次元可爱 ...","userSign":"","message":"类似 三体的同人短片 《水滴》？","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/44/17/441789.jpg","floor":"#5","id":"1472762","time":"2019-8-2 12:52","userId":"ubisoft","userName":"Ubisoft","userSign":"","message":"我喜欢这个梦","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/05/41/54176.jpg","floor":"#6","id":"1472779","time":"2019-8-2 13:20","userId":"light_44","userName":"lighthouse","userSign":"","message":"然后上班固米水了一贴<br><br>梦境真的会预知现实呢","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/00/34/3490.jpg","floor":"#7","id":"1472781","time":"2019-8-2 13:24","userId":"lhb5883","userName":"lhb5883-污🐱王VIP⑩","userSign":"(媛娇系是检验大法的唯一标准)","message":"记得长光卫星还摇过奖 指定拍一张卫星照片","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/31/34/313469.jpg","floor":"#8","id":"1473007","time":"2019-8-2 17:55","userId":"313469","userName":"Cedar","userSign":"(｡´-д-)","message":"梦中的人脸可以很清晰啊 尤其是认识的人..<br>我觉得不是潜意识的记